print("Function to calculate the mean and standard deviation")
## [1] "Function to calculate the mean and standard deviation"
MSD<-function(data) {
  avg<-mean(data)
  SD<-sd(data)
  c(avg, SD)
}

size_n<-30
sum_n<-77
sig<-2.5
alphaval<-0.025
z_val<-qnorm(1-alphaval)
x_bar<-size_n/sum_n
Lower<-x_bar-z_val*(sig/sqrt(size_n))
Upper<-x_bar+z_val*(sig/sqrt(size_n))
c(Lower, Upper)
## [1] -0.5049867  1.2842075

qqline(sal)

Cinterval<-function(data, conf.level) {
  n<-length(data)
  Tval=qt((1-conf.level)/2, n-1, lower.tail = FALSE)
  xbar=mean(data)
  sdx=sqrt(var(data)/n) 
  c(xbar-Tval*sdx, xbar+Tval*sdx)
}
Cinterval(sal, 0.95)
## [1] 46.85025 52.23308
